Ended up using something like this.

```python
@aiostream.operator
async def iterator_from_awaitable(coro):
    task = asyncio.ensure_future(coro)
    await task

    yield task.result()

@aiostream.operator
def stream_from_coroutines(*coroutines):
    iterators = [iterator_from_awaitable.raw(c) for c in coroutines]
    return aiostream.stream.merge.raw(*iterators)
```

