@jettify @vproman a pitfall that i encountered when replicating `sa` functionality:
The [asynchronous file descriptor](https://github.com/aio-libs/aiopg/blob/master/aiopg/connection.py#L112) such as available in aiopg, which is supported by [psycopg](http://initd.org/psycopg/docs/connection.html#connection.fileno) under the hood, Is Not supported by in pyodbc because of [this limitation](https://github.com/mkleehammer/pyodbc/issues/348#issuecomment-368080874)

